<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Template- Resume builder</title>
     <style>
   /* General Styles */
body, html {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #ffffff);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
}  

.container {
  overflow: hidden;
  max-width: 390px;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Semi-transparent white */  
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0px 15px 20px rgba(0,0,0,1);
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* Optional: light border */
  
}

.logo {
    width: 100px; /* Adjust width as necessary */
    height: 100px; /* Adjust height to keep aspect ratio */
    margin-bottom: 1px;
    display: block; /* Ensures image is displayed as a block element */
    margin-right: auto; /* Center the icon */
}

h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
}

p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #080808;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.t {
    color: #00FF00;
    font-size: 27px; /* Set font size to 20px */
    text-shadow: -1px -1px 0 #000,  
                 1px -1px 0 #000,
                 -1px 1px 0 #000,
                 1px 1px 0 #000;
}



/* Options Container */
.option-box {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 30px; /* Add gap between the boxes */
}

.option {
    background: transparent; /* Make background transparent */
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 45%;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline from links */
    color: inherit; /* Inherit text color */
}

.option:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
}

#a {
    width: 130px;
}

.icon {
    width: 100px; /* Adjust width as necessary */
    height: 80px; /* Adjust height to keep aspect ratio */
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: block; /* Ensures image is displayed as a block element */
    margin-left: auto; /* Center the icon */
    margin-right: auto; /* Center the icon */
}


h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    color: black;   
}

.option p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #060606;
}


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="Assets/images/logonxt.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Welcome to <span class="t">Template selection</span></h1>
        <p>You can create your ATS-friendly resume in two simple ways:</p>
        <div class="option-box">
            <a href="/resume1" class="option">
                <img src="Assets\images\one.png" alt="Add Credits Icon" class="icon" id="a"> <!-- Replace with your image path -->
                <h2>Enter your details in Blocks</h2>
                <p>Resume will be generated below for you</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/resume2" class="option">
                <img src="Assets\images\two.png" alt="Cloud Storage Icon" class="icon"> <!-- Replace with your image path -->
                <h2>Edit your existing resume</h2>
                <p> Simply update it with your information for a quick refresh.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    

    


   
</body>
</html>
